                        "text": "When a tzitzimitl\u2019s claw Strike deals damages to a living creature, the tzitzimitl gains 20 temporary Hit Points, and the target must succeed at a DC 41 Fortitude save or become <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">drained 2</a>. Further damage dealt by a tzitzimitl\u2019s claw Strike increases the value of the drained condition by 2 on a failed save, to a maximum of <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">drained 10</a>."
                    },
